<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>예약 상세 내역 | TravelMate</title>
  {{>partials/head-assets}}
  <link href="/css/account.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="page-body page-body-sans">
  {{>partials/header}}

  <main class="account-page account-page--detail">
    <div class="booking-detail-shell">
      <div class="booking-detail-breadcrumb">
        <a href="/mypage">마이페이지</a>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">chevron_right</span>
        <span>예약 상세 내역</span>
      </div>

      <div class="booking-detail-header">
        <div>
          <p class="booking-detail-header__label">Reservation Overview</p>
          <h1 class="booking-detail-header__title">예약 상세 내역</h1>
          <p class="booking-detail-header__subtitle">예약 번호: KR-20231024-88421</p>
        </div>
        <a class="account-button account-button--ghost" href="/mypage">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_back</span>
          마이페이지로 돌아가기
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="booking-detail-summary-grid">
        <article class="booking-detail-summary-card">
          <p class="booking-detail-summary-card__label">예약 상태</p>
          <div class="booking-detail-summary-card__value">
            <span class="booking-detail-summary-card__dot"></span>
            <strong>예약 확정</strong>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="booking-detail-summary-card">
          <p class="booking-detail-summary-card__label">예약 일자</p>
          <div class="booking-detail-summary-card__value">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">calendar_today</span>
            <strong>2023년 10월 24일</strong>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <section class="booking-detail-panel">
        <div class="booking-detail-panel__head">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">hotel</span>
          <h2>숙소 상세 정보</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="booking-detail-stay">
          <div class="booking-detail-stay__media"></div>
          <div class="booking-detail-stay__body">
            <div>
              <h3 class="booking-detail-stay__title">그랜드 하얏트 서울</h3>
              <p class="booking-detail-stay__address">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">location_on</span>
                서울특별시 용산구 소월로 322
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="booking-detail-meta-grid">
              <div class="booking-detail-meta-item">
                <span class="booking-detail-meta-item__label">체크인</span>
                <strong>2023.11.15 (수)</strong>
                <span>15:00 이후</span>
              </div>
              <div class="booking-detail-meta-item">
                <span class="booking-detail-meta-item__label">체크아웃</span>
                <strong>2023.11.17 (금)</strong>
                <span>11:00 이전</span>
              </div>
              <div class="booking-detail-meta-item">
                <span class="booking-detail-meta-item__label">인원 구성</span>
                <strong>성인 2명, 아동 1명</strong>
              </div>
              <div class="booking-detail-meta-item">
                <span class="booking-detail-meta-item__label">객실 타입</span>
                <strong>디럭스 킹 리버뷰</strong>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="booking-detail-panel">
        <div class="booking-detail-panel__head">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">payments</span>
          <h2>결제 정보</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="booking-detail-payment-list">
          <div class="booking-detail-payment-row booking-detail-payment-row--total">
            <span>총 결제 금액</span>
            <strong>745,000원</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="booking-detail-payment-row">
            <span>결제 수단</span>
            <span>현대카드 (4412-****-****-0123) / 일시불</span>
          </div>
          <div class="booking-detail-payment-row">
            <span>결제 일시</span>
            <span>2023.10.24 14:32:15</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="booking-detail-policy">
        <div class="booking-detail-policy__head">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">info</span>
          <h2>취소 및 환불 규정 안내</h2>
        </div>
        <ul class="booking-detail-policy__list">
          <li><strong>2023년 11월 12일 23:59까지</strong>는 무료 취소가 가능합니다.</li>
          <li>11월 13일 취소 시: 전체 금액의 50% 위약금 발생</li>
          <li>체크인 당일 및 노쇼(No-show): 환불 불가</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="booking-detail-actions">
        <a class="account-button account-button--primary" href="/mypage">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">list</span>
          마이 페이지로 돌아가기
        </a>
        <button class="account-button account-button--secondary" type="button">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">cancel</span>
          예약 취소 요청
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  {{>partials/footer}}
  {{>partials/scripts}}
</body>
</html>
